abstract: U.S. health officials said on Thursday two more deaths occurred since last week from a mysterious respiratory illness tied to vaping, taking the total toll to 54.
snippet: U.S. health officials said on Thursday two more deaths occurred since last week from a mysterious respiratory illness tied to vaping, taking the total toll to 54.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - U.S. health officials said on Thursday two more deaths occurred since last week from a mysterious respiratory illness tied to vaping, taking the total toll to 54.
headline_main: U.S. Vaping-Related Deaths Rise to 54, Hospitalizations to 2,506
headline_print_headline: U.S. Vaping-Related Deaths Rise to 54, Hospitalizations to 2,506

abstract: Five people were being treated for injuries after a shooting incident in central Moscow on Thursday evening near the FSB security services headquarters, Interfax news agency cited the health ministry as saying.
snippet: Five people were being treated for injuries after a shooting incident in central Moscow on Thursday evening near the FSB security services headquarters, Interfax news agency cited the health ministry as saying.
lead_paragraph: MOSCOW — Five people were being treated for injuries after a shooting incident in central Moscow on Thursday evening near the FSB security services headquarters, Interfax news agency cited the health ministry as saying.
headline_main: Five Wounded in Moscow Shooting, Receiving Treatment: Interfax Cites Health Ministry
headline_print_headline: Five Wounded in Moscow Shooting, Receiving Treatment: Interfax Cites Health Ministry

abstract: Lebanon's newly-named prime minister vowed on Thursday to form a government quickly that works to pull the country out of economic crisis and reassures people who have protested against the political class for two months.
snippet: Lebanon's newly-named prime minister vowed on Thursday to form a government quickly that works to pull the country out of economic crisis and reassures people who have protested against the political class for two months.
lead_paragraph: BEIRUT — Lebanon's newly-named prime minister vowed on Thursday to form a government quickly that works to pull the country out of economic crisis and reassures people who have protested against the political class for two months.
headline_main: Lebanon's New PM Diab Vows to Form Government Quickly
headline_print_headline: Lebanon's New PM Diab Vows to Form Government Quickly

abstract: More than 99% of U.S. President Donald Trump's television ads have focused on impeachment this year, according to an analysis that shows how central the topic has become for his re-election campaign.
snippet: More than 99% of U.S. President Donald Trump's television ads have focused on impeachment this year, according to an analysis that shows how central the topic has become for his re-election campaign.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — More than 99% of U.S. President Donald Trump's television ads have focused on impeachment this year, according to an analysis that shows how central the topic has become for his re-election campaign.
headline_main: Almost All of Trump's TV Campaign Ads Discuss Impeachment: Report
headline_print_headline: Almost All of Trump's TV Campaign Ads Discuss Impeachment: Report

abstract: The United States said new evidence and analysis of weapons debris recovered from an attack on Saudi oil facilities on Sept. 14 indicates the strike likely came from the north, reinforcing its earlier assessment that Iran was behind the offensive.
snippet: The United States said new evidence and analysis of weapons debris recovered from an attack on Saudi oil facilities on Sept. 14 indicates the strike likely came from the north, reinforcing its earlier assessment that Iran was behind the offensive.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The United States said new evidence and analysis of weapons debris recovered from an attack on Saudi oil facilities on Sept. 14 indicates the strike likely came from the north, reinforcing its earlier assessment that Iran was behind the offensive.
headline_main: Exclusive: U.S. Probe of Saudi Oil Attack Shows It Came From North-Report
headline_print_headline: Exclusive: U.S. Probe of Saudi Oil Attack Shows It Came From North-Report

abstract: The Wawa convenience store chain says a data breach may have collected debit and credit card information from thousands of customers.

abstract: President Donald Trump announced on Thursday that a Democratic U.S. lawmaker who opposed his party's move to impeach the Republican president was switching parties, a day after the House of Representatives approved articles of impeachment.
snippet: President Donald Trump announced on Thursday that a Democratic U.S. lawmaker who opposed his party's move to impeach the Republican president was switching parties, a day after the House of Representatives approved articles of impeachment.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Donald Trump announced on Thursday that a Democratic U.S. lawmaker who opposed his party's move to impeach the Republican president was switching parties, a day after the House of Representatives approved articles of impeachment.
headline_main: Trump Announces Democrat Van Drew Switching to Republican Party
headline_print_headline: Trump Announces Democrat Van Drew Switching to Republican Party

abstract: Peru's President Martin Vizcarra said he will seek to strengthen labor laws to take more "concrete action" against companies involved in workplace accidents after two teenaged employees died in a McDonald's Corp franchise at the weekend.
snippet: Peru's President Martin Vizcarra said he will seek to strengthen labor laws to take more "concrete action" against companies involved in workplace accidents after two teenaged employees died in a McDonald's Corp franchise at the weekend.
lead_paragraph: Lima (Reuters) - Peru's President Martin Vizcarra said he will seek to strengthen labor laws to take more "concrete action" against companies involved in workplace accidents after two teenaged employees died in a McDonald's Corp franchise at the weekend.
headline_main: Peru President Vows Tougher Sanctions for Labor Accidents After McDonald's Deaths
headline_print_headline: Peru President Vows Tougher Sanctions for Labor Accidents After McDonald's Deaths
